import React from 'react'
import Cart from '../Cart/Cart'
import AvailableMeals from './AvailableMeals'
import MealsSummary from './MealsSummary'

const Meals = (props) => {
  return (
    <React.Fragment>
      <MealsSummary />
      <AvailableMeals />
      <Cart />
    </React.Fragment>
  )
}

export default Meals
